    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape\u2014it still has that fresh car smell and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it is practically spotless inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to drop me a message if you want to come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
