      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 BMW M3 Coupe (E92). At its heart lies the S65 high-revving V8, delivering 414 hp with a soaring 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically flawless, featuring documented preventative rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides seamless torque transfer to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The EDC (Electronic Damper Control) chassis remains razor-sharp, with zero subframe fatigue or suspension bushing play. Meticulously preserved in Alpine",
      "price": 50000.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Single owner. Full service history. No accidents. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 44000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
