    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously maintained to satisfy the most discerning collector. The exterior boasts a showroom-quality finish with professional ceramic coating, showing zero dings, scratches, or rock chips. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and free of any creases or wear, with every electronic feature functioning exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is flawless; it has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive folder of records included. Always garage-kept and never driven in inclement weather, this car offers a factory-fresh experience that must be seen in person to be fully appreciated.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
