    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved to maintain its original factory luster. Every detail, from the immaculate interior appointments to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a standard of stewardship that is rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. This is an investment-grade acquisition intended for the discerning driver who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 43500.0,
